This project builds and packages the following components, each with their own licenses:

- TVHeadend: GPL-3.0 (https://github.com/tvheadend/tvheadend)
- FFmpeg: GPL-3.0+ when built with GPL libraries (https://ffmpeg.org/legal.html)
- Comskip: GPL-2.0 (https://github.com/erikkaashoek/Comskip)
- Intel libvpl: MIT (https://github.com/intel/libvpl)
- Picons: CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 (https://github.com/picons/picons)
- WebGrab++: Custom license (http://www.webgrabplus.com/)

The resulting Debian packages and Docker images are distributed under GPL-3.0
due to the inclusion of GPL-licensed components.

Build scripts and configuration files in this repository are available under
GPL-3.0 to maintain compatibility with the packaged software.
